Privacy Policy for Tiny Epochs

Information Collection and Use:

Tiny Epochs does not collect, store, or share any personal information. We respect your privacy and do not track you in any way.

Data Storage:

All game progress and settings are stored locally on your device only. No data is transmitted to external servers.

In-App Purchases:

In-app purchases are processed by Apple through the App Store. We do not have access to your payment information. All purchase data is handled securely by Apple according to their privacy policy.

Third-Party Services:

We do not use any third-party analytics, advertising, or tracking services.

Children's Privacy:

Our app does not knowingly collect any information from children. The game is designed to be safe for all ages.

Changes to This Policy:

We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page.

Developer: Appnovex
App: TinyEpochs
